Living Room
Lingering Spirit's Living Room: The kitchen is east to the room and the study is west. You can also go up the stairs. Talk to the butler.
#
#
Kitchen
Butcher's Kitchen: You can either go down to search the dark basement or west back to the living room.
#
#
Stairwell
Creaking Stairwell: There are pictures on the wall. Go down the stairs to return to the living room or continue north to enter the nursey.
#
#
Study
Study of Whispers: The only exit for the room is east towards the living room.
#
#
Nursery
Doll Playhouse Nursery: A music box with a twirling ballerina fills the quiet room offkey tune as creaky various kinds of dolls watch your every move. You can leave this room by heading south back to the stairwell.
#
#
Basement
Forgotten Screams Basement: The basement is dark, you can hear faded scream and cries. You can exit by going up to the kitchen. You will need to complete the ritual here to escape the haunted house.
#
#
Freedom
Congratulations! You have found freedom! You won the game! You can now exit the game with x.